thread.title: Bhavani Subramaniam

author: Bhavani Subramaniam
title: Bhavani Subramaniam
text: Best value car cover for me, easy to use website and chat facility was perfect when I had to use it regardless of other reviews here. They are an online company so if you must speak with someone or have an issue with using a chat facility/callback request then maybe go somewhere else. To save money on your insurance this is how they can pass savings onto the customer - in my opinion of course.
